cd bin;
mv SupportTool.exe SupportTool.bak;
ln -s EoCApp.exe SupportTool.exe;


Played the tutorial. No issues encountered like font issues, sound crackling, visual artifacts.

Runs quite smooth on ULTRA Settings.
